{"tid":2155560,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿聯酋及以色列歷史性協議 美國安顧問：川普應得諾貝爾和平獎","createTime":"2020-08-14T01:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T09:09:58.000Z","uid":28765,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"be2012359edd12d2d3d24fe90d529d479092fc9b","tid":2155560,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:02:35.000Z","msg":"2020-08-14 08:17:37<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕以色列與阿拉伯聯合大公國13日達成歷史性的和平協議，美國、阿聯和以色列發表了聯合聲明，稱3國同意以色列和阿聯之間的關係全面正常化。美國國安顧問歐布萊恩表示，美國總統川普為此應獲得諾貝爾和平獎。<br />\n<br />\n《THE HILL》報導，歐布萊恩週四表示，川普因在中東的努力，應獲得諾貝爾和平獎，並將以偉大的和平締造者被人們記得，去年聯合國也有記者對川普說，如果川普能調解巴基斯坦和印度之間，喀什米爾的主權爭端，就應該得到諾貝爾和平獎，當時川普表示，如果他們公平的授獎，那我會在很多事情上都得到諾貝爾獎。<br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3259891\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3259891&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBRy8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=eb1a0bc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3259891&h=432ebafa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3259891</a>"},{"pid":"1ef80e8a35b3f2781da4d01f0a223968360193d6","tid":2155560,"uid":221343,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:03:32.000Z","msg":"消滅到支那就值得攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5b1be4a0c53c412194795dd2f93461bf9c5d69","tid":2155560,"uid":199670,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:03:37.000Z","msg":"打尻支那 消滅支那 咁就世界美好 咁就真係值得攞獎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38ba3fe546aec9d2c86a9242334a17b3ac28f79","tid":2155560,"uid":101328,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:04:14.000Z","msg":"比黑人嗰個拎番黎比侵侵"},{"pid":"b85f54780e7457a50b6aa0035d